4 SYNOPSIS:
5 An autocycle is a type of motor vehicle with
6 three wheels.
7 Under existing law, an individual operating an
8 autocycle is exempt from motorcycle protective gear
9 requirements when operating the vehicle.
10 This bill would require the operator of an
11 autocycle to wear protective headgear and shoes in
12 compliance with motorcycle protective gear requirements
13 when operating or riding in the autocycle.
